    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>什么是SokoSolitaire?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SokoSolitaire是一款独特的游戏，结合了推箱子和纸牌元素。运用您的智慧来称霸每个关卡，将卡牌推到其目的地，同时在必要时堆叠或翻转卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>推动卡牌</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318680/extras/e12fd1b72795110c9b5674ef2d4a5286.poster.avif?t=1757579576\" width=540 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318680/extras/e12fd1b72795110c9b5674ef2d4a5286.webm?t=1757579576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318680/extras/e12fd1b72795110c9b5674ef2d4a5286.mp4?t=1757579576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>每个关卡的目标是将所有卡牌推到其目的地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>灵感来自纸牌</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318680/extras/7bdd6f9827da117a5a6c8fc655b4b9f9.poster.avif?t=1757579576\" width=526 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318680/extras/7bdd6f9827da117a5a6c8fc655b4b9f9.webm?t=1757579576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318680/extras/7bdd6f9827da117a5a6c8fc655b4b9f9.mp4?t=1757579576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>来克服其他益智游戏中没有的独特纸牌元素吧。您可以堆叠、翻转，或者改变卡牌的花色等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318680/extras/b17c0f384a2db8f1565cdefadf3f2a7f.avif?t=1757579576\" width=621 height=170 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 个独家制作的关卡 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无限撤消 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不喜欢您正在玩的关卡？ 跳过它！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推箱子和纸牌的创新组合 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色盲模式三基色二色性单色 </p></li></ul>",
